# Visual Style Guide

Use **`docs/design-language/FOUNDATION.mdc`** as the merged authority and **`docs/VISUAL_STYLE_GUIDE.mdc`** as the short entry point for visual communication work.

## New-regime default

Use the NYCTA-inspired transit/signage system for:

- governance maps
- framework diagrams
- route maps
- authoritative charts
- future campaign graphics for the new era

## Legacy satire mode

Use the whiteboard/editorial-cartoon system for:

- retrospective critique
- old-regime satire
- workaround humor
- governance-failure diagrams

## Avoid

- generic SaaS gradients
- neon AI styling
- interchangeable startup illustration systems
